(CGMCC 3.20159). a Yellow colony on a fruiting body of 
<taxonomicName box="[1074,1180,1882,1903]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Boletaceae" genus="Boletus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Boletales" pageId="10" pageNumber="38" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="undetermined">
